Mapinformations:
****************

This map is about a german musicals names "Tanz der Vampire" [GER] (Eng.: "Dance
of the vampire"). But in this luxus-jail isn't only the musical! 

You can find there a swimplace. Its look like in a junge and there is very big tree 
where you can go up and jump in the water. You can see behind the big tree a 
very big waterslide!

In one room you see a aquarium, where you can go in from the room over it.

There is a footballroom. You can change between 3 floors and 8 balls.
Goals come up, when you press a button.

You can visit a big room with a lot of crates. You can destroy them. It's funny!

The weapon-room was blow upped from any person and the securityguy is killed. You
can go to the weapon-room throug a destroyed elevator.

The CT's start in the weapon-room and can either go directly to the cells or throug
the destroyed elevator in an other room.

The T's start in there cells. There aren't any weapons in.

Hafe Fun & Good Look in my Map and enjoy my fantasie!

Hello everyone .. After a long time I made a remake of my famous jail map underfoot. Is it incorporated many new features such as texture change and the creation of full HDR compilation. Next, I added a secret room at the entrance to which it adds 666 to your score and play a little faster song :-) (do not think that to get it so easily ..). I have also added two passes in a cell to another cell, making it harder to detect on CT who has a gun and who does not :-) and many other interesting things such as a shaft, which must be broken rib after rib. On this map I had mainly depend for demanding players that they liked more than the previous, slightly less lagging version :-). If you find an error in my map, write me a message and I'll definitely fix it.

### 2072. Revolution in the technologies for the world. One scientist has invented a virtual reality project, which practically does not differ from reality itself. His idea was immediately bought by the name of a famous developer -BlackHawk-, or we can call him Black. He has so long wanted to implement something like virtual prison for prisoners, which they will have a choice between freedom and death. But the impetus for that was to date from the game mod CS:S, Jail Mod. But the meaning of then current Jail Mod and virtual Jail, was quite different. In "Virtua Jail", as the prisoners were to serve the real criminals connected to the computer and are in a virtual world. In the role as prison guards should be trained to act people, real experts in their field, and at the request of and for the well-paid amount for the jailers can make anyone. The rules of the prison were much harder: there died - he died here, while this rule applies only to prisoners. And this is without taking into account the individual rules, which are discussed here will not be mentioned. However, if you managed to survive, you get an early release. The first location for the project "Virtua Jail" performed by the owner of this project, Black. He's going to create something where the prisoners for the last time will be have fun, or to show their strength and confidence. But only the best of the best will be able to beat a jailers in this game, who as always have an advantage ...
